metadata.description: Yoko was born without eyes. But she didn't know that other people had eyes, her parents told her that all people didn't have eyes either. She was home schooled and not allowed to go outside. Over the years, Yoko learned to hear the world around her very well. She doesn't even need eyesight. One day she overheard her parents talking about their neighbor. Her father said: "One eye isn't the end of the world, maybe it's even handy." That night Yoko's world was turned upside down, she learned that other people have eyesight! But she didn't know the whole truth...
